I'm quite the daredevil-not to mention nudist-so if PlayboyTV ever brings back Badass, I'm gonna be one of the first models they call! "With hard work, perseverance, and more importantly, patience, anything is possible," says Khloe, beaming. "With Playboy Plus, I made my dreams my reality!"
